---
description: Rules for deciding where to place reusable components in a Next.js 14 project.
globs: **/app/**/_components/**/*.*, **/app/**/global/**/*.*,**/components/global/**/*.*
alwaysApply: true


- Component placement rule: Only create a reusable component inside a global folder if it has potential to be used in multiple places. Otherwise, create it inside the `_components` folder of the specific route, or ask me before deciding the location.

